WIP…

To build, run:

./bootstrap --bootstrap-sync --force --skip-po

./configure CFLAGS="-g3 -O2 -DFORTIFY_SOURCE=2 -fsanitize=undefined -fsanitize-undefined-trap-on-error -fsanitize=address -Wall -Wextra"

make -j

make -j check

Unfortunately address sanitizer detects memory leaks in mpfr, so we
can’t use it.